snippet.title: Lambeosaurus Gameplay | Showcase - Dinosaur King Arcade Game 恐竜キング
snippet.description:
Dinosaur King Showcase 16 - Lambeosaurus
ft. Ursula VS Dr.Z
Lambeosaurus ランベオサウルス 賴氏龍 / 蘭伯龍
Element : Grass 草
Strength : 1800
Name Meaning : Lambe's Lizard
Length: 15m
[ http://dinosaurking.wikia.com/wiki/Lambeosaurus ]

& Seismosaurus  of Big Foot Assault

VS Stegosaurus & Super Alpha Kentrosaurus

I gonna make a series of dinosaur showcase videos including moves and super moves for documentary of dinosaur king
Full Showcase Playlist ( https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLzSUN2_e928Okhjm6IE58QYn_gLUeOBQ1 )
